name: "Creepy Joe (Cold Life)" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Crayon and sticker collage on cardstock with digital embellishments, color, and moshing.] Creepy Joe crawled along the floor, searching for his next victim, but when a quantum fluctuation appeared directly beneath his feet, he found himself transported to a dimension outside of time and right next door to space. (He didn't like it...) This event lasted for approximately 23 minutes (in our time) but (to Joe) it FELT like years... ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
